__comments__.info: This file contains the fixed Holy Days etc. in the Church of England calendar, taken from 'The Calendar' in Common Worship.
__comments__.warning_months: Months start at 0 as they do in Javascript. January = 0, December = 11.
__comments__.warning_conents: This file does not include variable Holy Days such as Easter, as their dates are not fixed.
